{"sn2.5:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 2.5 ","sn2.5:0.2":"1. Pathamavagga ","sn2.5:0.3":"Damalisutta ","sn2.5:1.1":"Savatthinidanam. ","sn2.5:1.2":"Atha kho damali devaputto abhikkantaya rattiya abhikkantavanno kevalakappam jetavanam obhasetva yena bhagava tenupasankami; upasankamitva bhagavantam abhivadetva ekamantam atthasi. ","sn2.5:1.3":"Ekamantam thito kho damali devaputto bhagavato santike imam gatham abhasi: ","sn2.5:2.1":"“Karaniyametam brahmanena, ","sn2.5:2.2":"Padhanam akilasuna; ","sn2.5:2.3":"Kamanam vippahanena, ","sn2.5:2.4":"Na tenasisate bhavan”ti. ","sn2.5:3.1":"“Natthi kiccam brahmanassa, ","sn2.5:3.2":"(damaliti bhagava) ","sn2.5:3.3":"Katakicco hi brahmano; ","sn2.5:3.4":"Yava na gadham labhati nadisu, ","sn2.5:3.5":"Ayuhati sabbagattebhi jantu; ","sn2.5:3.6":"Gadhanca laddhana thale thito yo, ","sn2.5:3.7":"Nayuhati paragato hi sova. ","sn2.5:4.1":"Esupama damali brahmanassa, ","sn2.5:4.2":"Khinasavassa nipakassa jhayino; ","sn2.5:4.3":"Pappuyya jatimaranassa antam, ","sn2.5:4.4":"Nayuhati paragato hi so”ti. "}